                <note rend="inline" type="source">393.1123 Winterle/3: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in China</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Johnson</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1935-09-23T11:00:00-04:00"
                            >September 23, 1935—11 a.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>3. Your 7, September 21, noon, and Chefoo’s September 21, 4 p.m., to you.
                    Department wondering why Chefoo has not lodged and you have not recommended
                    lodging charge against Japanese policeman. Please inform Department
                    immediately.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
